{
  "stem": "18626.12",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to the platform.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The same routine was, I had to point with my finger and show him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the prosecutor started asking me questions about Moll.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What type of person he was, what type of man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had to tell them the truth, you know, that Moll, he used to kill the prisoners on the working place where we were working.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He couldn't stay a minute still without trying to kill a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He took prisoners.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He beat them to death, and he pushed them in the cement, because they were building that big factory and it was so much cement.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The tops that they were-- they didn't want any, you know, no bomb to go through.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he used to throw in prisoners in the cement and bury them [? there, ?] and just write in the report, prisoner drowned in cement.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If they are gonna-- maybe they did break all the cement work, but we are working there weeks and months.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe they took out the prisoners from there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If not, the prisoners are laying dead in the cement with no mercy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they used to giggle and laugh and call his comerades, the other Germans, to show them what he did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't ask me absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, a farmer came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A civilian, a farmer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the farmer had a farm near where I was liberated, near-- close to Bad Tolz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was testifying against Moll.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he says, he cannot sleep nights, the farmer said, knowing it, that he hears maybe 30 or 40 prisoners shot on his property in his yard in his-- on his lawn.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, how do you know who killed them?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
